'''Docking Bay 331''' was one of many [[Hangar/Legends|docking bays]] in [[Karfeddion Spaceport]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Karfeddion/Legends|Karfeddion]]. Prior to the [[Eriadu Trade Summit]] in [[33 BBY/Legends|33 BBY]], [[Arwen Cohl|Cohl]], [[Boiny]], and [[Lope (individual)|Lope]] rendezvoused with several [[Nebula Front/Legends|Nebula Front]] members in the bay before embarking on their attempted assassination mission of [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Chancellor]] [[Finis Valorum/Legends|Finis Valorum]].

